               cmake (>= 3.14),
               build-essential,
               pkg-config
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://github.com/cm-jones/libdsc
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/cm-jones/libdsc.git
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/cm-jones/libdsc

Package: libdsc0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Generic data structure containers for C - runtime library
 libdsc is a free and open-source C library that provides generic
 implementations of various containers from the C++ Standard Library.
 The project aims to bring modern container functionality to C programming
 with memory-safe, well-tested implementations.
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

Package: libdsc-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libdsc0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Generic data structure containers for C - development files
 libdsc is a free and open-source C library that provides generic
 implementations of various containers from the C++ Standard Library.
 The project aims to bring modern container functionality to C programming
 with memory-safe, well-tested implementations.
 .
 This package contains the development files (headers, static library,
 pkg-config file, and CMake configuration).
